high_descs: Turn left and walk to the table then turn right.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the sink turning left to face it when you get there.
Wash the knife in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Back up a step so you can use the drawer in front of you.
Open the drawer that's to the left of the sink and put the knife in there and close it again.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to the white table, then turn right and walk up to the small black shelving unit to the left of the counter.
Pick up the large metal knife that is to the left of the sponge on top of the black shelving unit.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean knife.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and take a step towards the white table, turn right again to face the counter.
Open the leftmost drawer below the counter and put the clean knife inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a large clean knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left walk forward then turn right facing the small black shelf
Pick up the knife on the shelf
Turn right and head to the sink
Put the knife in the sink and rinse it
Pick up the knife in the sink and head to the left side drawer of the sink
Open the drawer and put in the clean knife
anns.task_desc: Put the clean knife in the sink drawer
